l Scout','C','{1}{W}','2','2','1',NULL,'{4}, {T}: Search your library for a Rebel permanent card with converted mana cost 3 or less and put it onto the battlefield. Then shuffle your library.','#_The people of Amrou were scattered by war and driven into hiding. Scouts maintain the beacon fires that signal "return" and "home."_#',NULL,'Quinton Hoover','1','3.5',NULL,'W',NULL,'0.03','0.16','1.08',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W','安罗斥候',NULL,'Éclaireuse amroue','Amrou-Späher','Esploratrice di Amrou','アムローの偵察兵','Batedor Amrou','Разведчик Амру','Exploradora de Amrou',NULL,'生物～洁英／反抗军／斥候',NULL,'Créature : sangami et rebelle et éclaireur','Kreatur — Kithkin, Rebell, Späher','Creatura — Esploratore Ribelle Kithkin','クリーチャー ― キスキン・レベル・スカウト','Criatura — Batedor Rebelde Kithkin','Существо — Кискин Повстанец Разведчик','Criatura — Explorador rebelde kithkin',NULL,'{4}，{T}：从你的牌库中搜寻一张总法术力费用等于或小于3的反抗军牌，并将其放置进场。 然后将你的牌库洗牌。',NULL,'{4}, {T} : Cherchez dans votre bibliothèque une carte de rebelle avec un coût converti de mana de 3 ou moins et mettez-la en jeu. Mélangez ensuite votre bibliothèque.','{4}, {T}: Durchsuche deine Bibliothek nach einer Rebellenkarte mit umgewandelten Manakosten von 3 oder weniger und bringe sie ins Spiel. Mische danach deine Bibliothek.','{4}, {T}: Passa in rassegna il tuo grimorio per una carta Ribelle con costo di mana convertito pari o inferiore a 3 e mettila in gioco. Poi rimescola il tuo grimorio.','{4}, {T}：あなたのライブラリーから、点数で見たマナ・コストが３以下のレベル・カードを１枚探し、それを場に出す。 その後あなたのライブラリーを切り直す。','{4}, {T}: Procure em seu grimório por um card do tipo Rebelde com custo de mana convertido menor ou igual a 3 e coloque-o em jogo. Depois, embaralhe seu grimório.','{4}, {T}: Поищите в вашей библиотеке карту Повстанца с конвертированной мана-стоимостью не более 3 и положите ее в игру. Затем перемешайте вашу библиотеку.','{4}, {T}: Busca en tu biblioteca una carta de Rebelde con coste de maná convertido de 3 o menos y ponla en juego. Luego baraja tu biblioteca.',NULL,'#_安罗人民离散四方以避战火。 斥候则看守分别代表了「避难」与「返乡」的信标火焰。_#',NULL,'#_La population d''Amrou fut éparpillée par la guerre et forcée à se cacher. Les éclaireurs attisaient les grands feux qui signalaient le retour et le foyer._#','#_Der Krieg hatte das Volk von Amrou in alle Himmelsrichtungen verstreut und in Verstecke getrieben. Späher kümmerten sich um die Leuchtfeuer, die kommt und heim signalisierten._#','#_La guerra disperse il popolo di Amrou e lo costrinse a nascondersi. Gli esploratori tennero vivi i fuochi di segnalazione che indicavano il ritorno a casa._#','#_アムローの人々は戦争で散り散りになり、隠れ住まざるをえなくなった。 偵察隊は「本国へ」と「帰れ」の信号の炎を炊き続けた。_#','#_O povo de Amrou foi disperso pela guerra e forçado a esconder-se. Os batedores mantiveram suas fogueiras de sinalização que indicavam "retorno" e "casa"._#','#_Рассеянные войной люди Амру были вынуждены скрываться. Разведчики с нетерпением ждали сигнальных огней — "обратно" и "домой"._#','#_El pueblo de Amrou fue desperdigado por la guerra y obligado a esconderse. Los exploradores mantenían los fuegos de las almenaras que señalaban regreso y hogar._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('113509','Amrou Seekers','TSP','Creature — Kithkin Rebel','C','{2}{W}','3','2','2',NULL,'Amrou Seekers can''t be blocked except by artifact creatures and/or white creatures.','#_The paradise of Amrou Haven had become a field of cinders. Its people struggled to survive, hoping to see visions of its past in the strange storms that quickly passed._#',NULL,'Quinton Hoover','2','3.115',NULL,'W',NULL,'0.04','0.16','1.14',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W','安罗追寻者',NULL,'Chercheurs amrous','Amrou-Sucher','Cercatori di Amrou','アムローの求道者','Perseguidores de Amrou','Исследователи Амру','Buscadores de Amrou',NULL,'生物～洁英／反抗军',NULL,'Créature : sangami et rebelle','Kreatur — Kithkin, Rebell','Creatura — Ribelle Kithkin','クリーチャー ― キスキン・レベル','Criatura — Rebelde Kithkin','Существо — Кискин Повстанец','Criatura — Rebelde kithkin',NULL,'安罗追寻者只能被神器和／或白色生物阻挡。',NULL,'Les Chercheurs amrous ne peuvent pas être bloqués excepté par des créatures-artefacts et/ou des créatures blanches.','Die Amrou-Sucher können nur von weißen und/oder Artefaktkreaturen geblockt werden.','I Cercatori di Amrou non possono essere bloccati tranne che da creature artefatto e/o creature bianche.','アムローの求道者は、アーティファクト・クリーチャーでも白のクリーチャーでもないクリーチャーにはブロックされない。','Perseguidores de Amrou só pode ser bloqueado por criaturas artefato e/ou criaturas brancas.','Исследователи Амру могут быть блокированы только артефактными существами и/или белыми существами.','Los Buscadores de Amrou no pueden ser bloqueados excepto por criaturas artefacto y/o criatura blancas.',NULL,'#_曾如仙境的安罗庇护地已化为遍野灰烬。 其间人民挣扎求生，希望能见到奇异风暴中惊鸿一瞥的过往美景。_#',NULL,'#_Le paradis qu''avait été le Sanctuaire d''Amrou n''était plus qu''un champ de cendres. Son peuple luttait pour survivre, espérant retrouver des visions de son passé dans les étranges tempêtes._#','#_Einst war Amrouhaven ein Paradies gewesen, jetzt war nur noch Asche übrig. Die Bewohner bemühten sich zu überleben und suchten Visionen der Vergangenheit in den seltsamen Stürmen, die schnell vorbeizogen._#','#_Il paradiso del Rifugio di Amrou era diventato un campo coperto di cenere. La sua gente si sforzava di sopravvivere, nella speranza di scorgere visioni del suo passato nelle strane tempeste che passavano rapidamente._#','#_アムローヘイヴンの楽園は消し炭の野と化した。 そこに住んでいた人々は、あっという間に過ぎ去っていった奇妙な嵐の中に浮かんだ過去の幻視を捕らえることを願い、必死に生き延びようとしていた。_#','#_O paraíso de Porto Amrou tornara-se um campo de cinzas As pessoas lutavam para sobreviver, na esperança de ter visões de seus passados nas estranhas tempestades que rapidamente se dissipavam._#','#_Блаженные Небеса Амру превратились в поля золы. Этот народ боролся за выживание в надежде увидеть видения прошлого в чужих штормах, быстро проносящихся мимо._#','#_El paraíso del Refugio Amrou se convirtió en un campo de cenizas. Su gente lucha por sobrevivir, esperando ver visiones de su pasado en las extrañas tormentas que pasan rápidamente._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('113505','Ancestral Vision','TSP','Sorcery','R',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Suspend 4—{U} #_(Rather than cast this card from your hand, pay {U} and exile it with four time counters on it. At the beginning of your upkeep, remove a time counter. When the last is removed, cast it without paying its mana cost.)_#£Target player draws three cards.',NULL,NULL,'Mark Poole','48','4.317','£6/7/2013: You can exile a card in your hand using suspend any time you could cast that card. Consider its card type, any effect that affects when you could cast it (such as flash) and any other effects that could stop you from casting it (such as Meddling Mage’s effect) to determine if and when you can do this. Whether or not you could actually complete all steps in casting the card is irrelevant. For example, you can exile a card with suspend that has no mana cost or requires a target even if no legal targets are available at that time.£6/7/2013: Exiling a card with suspend isn’t casting that card. This action doesn’t use the stack and can’t be responded to.£6/7/2013: If the spell requires any targets, those targets are chosen when the spell is finally cast, not when it’s exiled.£6/7/2013: If the first triggered ability of suspend (the one that removes time counters) is countered, no time counter is removed. The ability will trigger again during the card’s owner’s next upkeep.£6/7/2013: When the last time counter is removed, the second triggered ability of suspend will trigger. It doesn’t matter why the last time counter was removed or what effect removed it.£6/7/2013: If the second triggered ability of suspend (the one that lets you cast the card) is countered, the card can’t be cast. It remains exiled with no time counters on it, and it’s no longer suspended.£6/7/2013: As the second triggered ability resolves, you must cast the card if able. Timing restrictions based on the card’s type are ignored.£6/7/2013: If you can’t cast the card, perhaps because there are no legal targets available, it remains exiled with no time counters on it, and it’s no longer suspended.£6/7/2013: If the spell has any mandatory additional costs, you must pay those if able. However, if an additional cost includes a mana payment, you are forced to pay that cost only if there’s enough mana in your mana pool at the time you cast the spell. You aren’t forced to activate any mana abilities, although you may do so if you wish.£6/7/2013: A creature cast using suspend will enter the battlefield with haste. It will have haste until another player gains control of it (or, in some rare cases, gains control of the creature spell itself).£6/7/2013: Although originally printed with a characteristic-defining ability that defined its color, this card now has a color indicator. This color indicator can’t be affected by text-changing effects (such as the one created by Crystal Spray), although color-changing effects can still overwrite it.£9/20/2016: This has no mana cost, which means its mana cost can’t be paid for effects such as replicate from Djinn Illuminatus or flashback from Snapcaster Mage.','U',NULL,'12.5','21.24','53',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'U','先人的预视',NULL,'Vision ancestrale','Vision der Ahnen','Visione Ancestrale','祖先の幻視','Visão Ancestral','Родовое Видение','Visión ancestral',NULL,'法术',NULL,'Rituel','Hexerei','Stregoneria','ソーサリー','Feitiço','Волшебство','Conjuro',NULL,'先人的预视是蓝色。£延缓4～{U}（除了从你手上使用此牌，你能支付{U}并将此牌移出对战，且上面有四个计时指示物。 在你的维持开始时，从其上移去一个计时指示物。 当你移去最后一个时，则使用它且不需支付其法术力费用。）£目标牌手抓三张牌。',NULL,'La Vision ancestrale est bleue.£Suspension 4 — {U} #_(Plutôt que jouer cette carte depuis votre main, payez {U} et retirez-la de la partie avec quatre marqueurs « temps » sur elle. Au début de votre entretien, retirez un marqueur « temps ». Quand vous retirez le dernier, jouez cette carte sans payer son coût de mana.)_#£Le joueur ciblé pioche trois cartes.','Die Vision der Ahnen ist blau.£Aussetzen 4 — {U} #_(Statt diese Karte aus deiner Han